'''Infobox game''' - Comprehensive game information box template for games.darkrepos.com

==Description==

A modern infobox template supporting:
* Multiple game versions (original, remakes, ports)
* Multiple regional titles (Japanese, English, European)
* Multiple release dates by region
* Multiple publishers by region
* ROM technical specifications
* Comprehensive metadata

==Usage==

<pre>
{{Infobox game
| title           = Primary English title
| title_jp        = Japanese title (optional)
| title_jp_romaji = Romanized Japanese title (optional)
| title_alt       = Other alternate titles (optional)

| image           = Box art image filename
| image_caption   = Image caption (optional)

| developer       = Development company
| publisher       = Primary publisher (or use regional)
| publisher_jp    = Japanese publisher (optional)
| publisher_na    = North American publisher (optional)
| publisher_eu    = European publisher (optional)

| platform        = Primary platform (NES, SNES, GBA, etc.)
| platforms       = Additional platforms for ports/remakes

| release         = Simple release date (or use regional)
| release_jp      = Japan release date (optional)
| release_na      = North America release date (optional)
| release_eu      = Europe release date (optional)
| release_au      = Australia release date (optional)

| genre           = Game genre(s)
| players         = Number of players
| modes           = Game modes (single-player, multiplayer, etc.)

| mapper          = ROM mapper/memory controller
| rom_size        = PRG ROM size
| chr_size        = CHR ROM size (if applicable)
| ram_size        = Work RAM / Save RAM size
| sram            = Save RAM size (battery-backed)
| mirroring       = Screen mirroring type

| series          = Game series name (optional)
| predecessor     = Previous game in series (optional)
| successor       = Next game in series (optional)
}}
</pre>

==Parameters==

===Title Parameters===
{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Parameter !! Required !! Description
|-
| title || Yes || Primary English/localized title
|-
| title_jp || No || Original Japanese title in Japanese script
|-
| title_jp_romaji || No || Romanized Japanese title
|-
| title_alt || No || Other alternate titles (regional variants, subtitles)
|}

===Media Parameters===
{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Parameter !! Required !! Description
|-
| image || No || Box art or title screen image filename
|-
| image_caption || No || Caption for the image
|}

===Development Parameters===
{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Parameter !! Required !! Description
|-
| developer || Yes || Development company/studio
|-
| publisher || Yes* || Primary publisher (*or use regional publishers)
|-
| publisher_jp || No || Publisher in Japan
|-
| publisher_na || No || Publisher in North America
|-
| publisher_eu || No || Publisher in Europe
|}

===Platform Parameters===
{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Parameter !! Required !! Description
|-
| platform || Yes || Primary console platform
|-
| platforms || No || Additional platforms (for ports, remakes, Virtual Console, etc.)
|}

===Release Date Parameters===
{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Parameter !! Required !! Description
|-
| release || Yes* || Simple release date (*or use regional dates)
|-
| release_jp || No || Japan release date
|-
| release_na || No || North America release date
|-
| release_eu || No || Europe release date
|-
| release_au || No || Australia release date
|}

===Gameplay Parameters===
{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Parameter !! Required !! Description
|-
| genre || Yes || Game genre(s)
|-
| players || No || Number of players supported
|-
