|-
| successor || No || Next game in the series
|}

==Example: Simple Game==

<pre>
{{Infobox game
| title     = Dragon Warrior
| developer = Chunsoft
| publisher = Enix (JP), Nintendo (NA)
| platform  = NES
| release   = May 27, 1986
| genre     = RPG
| players   = 1
| mapper    = UNROM
| rom_size  = 64 KB
}}
</pre>

